<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <title>SQL Lab | Vehicle Sensor Analysis</title>

    <!-- Prism Syntax Highlighting -->
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/prism/1.29.0/themes/prism-tomorrow.min.css">

    <style>
        :root {
            --bg: #0f172a;
            --text: #f8fafc;
            --accent: #38bdf8;
            --card-bg: #1e293b;
        }

        body {
            background: var(--bg);
            color: var(--text);
            font-family: system-ui, sans-serif;
            padding: 40px;
            line-height: 1.6;
        }

        .container {
            max-width: 900px;
            margin: auto;
        }

        .back-link {
            color: var(--accent);
            text-decoration: none;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            display: inline-block;
            font-weight: 500;
        }

        h1 {
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }

        h3 {
            margin-top: 40px;
            border-left: 4px solid var(--accent);
            padding-left: 10px;
        }

        /* Buttons */
        .btn {
            display: inline-block;
            padding: 12px 22px;
            background: var(--accent);
            color: #000;
            border-radius: 6px;
            text-decoration: none;
            font-weight: bold;
            margin: 20px 0;
            transition: 0.2s ease;
        }

        .btn:hover {
            opacity: 0.85;
        }

        /* Image Hover Zoom */
        .analysis-plot {
            transition: transform 0.4s cubic-bezier(0.165, 0.84, 0.44, 1);
            cursor: zoom-in;
            display: block;
            margin: 30px auto;
            max-width: 100%;
            border-radius: 8px;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 6px rgba(0,0,0,0.3);
        }

        .analysis-plot:hover {
            transform: scale(1.08);
            box-shadow: 0 20px 40px rgba(0,0,0,0.6);
            z-index: 999;
            position: relative;
        }

        /* Code blocks */
        pre {
            background: var(--card-bg);
            padding: 15px;
            border-radius: 8px;
            overflow-x: auto;
        }
    </style>
</head>

<body>
<div class="project-card">
  <div class="card-header">
    <h3>🛰️ Radar Antenna Analysis</h3>
    <span class="tag">RF Signal Processing</span>
  </div>
  
  <img src="plot_RL_radarBands.png" alt="S11 Return Loss Plot" class="card-img">
  
  <div class="card-body">
    <p>Automated pipeline for converting raw Touchstone/CSV data into actionable RF metrics. Features resonance detection at 77 GHz and radiation pattern visualization.</p>
    
    <div class="skills-chips">
      <span>Python</span>
      <span>Pandas</span>
      <span>Matplotlib</span>
    </div>
    
    <a href="https://github.com/montahabouezzed-sys/RF-Signal-Processing-Antenna-Analysis" class="btn">View on GitHub</a>
  </div>
</div>

<style>
  .project-card {
    background: #1e293b;
    border: 1px solid #334155;
    border-radius: 12px;
    color: white;
    width: 350px;
    font-family: sans-serif;
    overflow: hidden;
    transition: transform 0.3s ease;
  }
  .project-card:hover { transform: translateY(-5px); }
  .card-header { padding: 15px; display: flex; justify-content: space-between; align-items: center; }
  .tag { background: #38bdf8; font-size: 10px; padding: 4px 8px; border-radius: 20px; color: #0f172a; font-weight: bold; }
  .card-img { width: 100%; height: auto; border-bottom: 1px solid #334155; }
  .card-body { padding: 15px; }
  .skills-chips span { font-size: 11px; background: #334155; padding: 2px 8px; border-radius: 4px; margin-right: 5px; }
  .btn { display: block; text-align: center; background: white; color: black; text-decoration: none; padding: 10px; border-radius: 6px; margin-top: 15px; font-weight: bold; }
</style>
</body>
</html>
